br/>**1 trip offered for every 5000 Gold packages purchased. For contest details, <a href="/?area=HL2GOLD_contest">click here</a>.<br/><br/></li></li></li></li></li></li></li></li></li></li></li></li></li></ul><br/>','CSS,Steam,HL2,Counter-Strike,Day of Defeat');
